<html>
  <head>
    <style>
      body { font-family: Arial, sans-serif; line-height: 1.6; color: #333; }
      .container { max-width: 600px; margin: 0 auto; padding: 20px; border: 1px
      solid #ddd; border-radius: 5px; background-color: #f9f9f9; } .btn {
      display: inline-block; background-color: #007bff; color: #fff;
      text-decoration: none; padding: 10px 20px; border-radius: 5px; margin-top:
      20px; } .btn:hover { background-color: #0056b3; }
    </style>
  </head>
  <body>
    <div class='container'>
      <h2>Password Reset Request</h2>
      <p>Hi {{username}},</p>
      <p>
        We received a request to reset your password. Click the button below to
        reset your password:
      </p>
      <p>
        <a href='{{resetLink}}' class='btn'>Reset Password</a>
      </p>
      <p>
        If you didn't request this, you can safely ignore this email. Your
        password will not be changed unless you click the link above.
      </p>
      <p>Best regards,</p>
      <p>The Mystery Chat Team</p>
    </div>
  </body>
</html>